title: TVS Motor launches Apache RTR 165 RP at Rs 1.45 lakh
description: "Born of racing lineage, the TVS Apache RTR 165 RP is the first product under the Race Performance series product portfolio," TVS Motor Company Head (Marketing Premium Business) Meghashyam Dighole said. The collectable product offers an array of premium features with cutting-edge technology for performance motorcycling enthusiasts in India, he added.
